modName: Daedric Armor Plus Battleaxe Batch File
summary: Hey, You want a set of Daedric Armour Plus a Battleaxe? You do? Well here you are.
descriptionHtml:
A batch file i made that gives you a full set of Daedric Armor, A Daedric Battleax, and fortifies your carry weight to 9000 or something.
Go into that nifty Console device and type bat daedricarmor to retrive your stuff!
For installation please place this file into your skyrim folder. not in data, just skyrim.
author: OblivionBeaver
